# Testing

## Automated (Ren'Py testcases)

- **File**: game/test_eevee_clues.rpy. Data and Logic layer only (no UI automation).
- **Run**: From project root (parent of game/): `renpy "path/to/Eevee Clues" test`. Or launcher "Run Testcases" (refresh launcher after adding first test).
- **Gate**: All testcases must pass before deploy. Fix failures or relax assertions only with justification.
- **Syntax**: testcase Name: (identifier, no quotes). Block: description "...", parameter x = [...], then `$` and assert eval(...). Button text style uses _text child (e.g. game_action_button_text), not text_idle_color on button.

